sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer (Frontend)
    participant A as Artist (Frontend)
    participant API as Backend API

    C->>API: POST /quotations (type=OPEN, description, location...)
    API-->>C: 201 Created (quotationId)

    A->>API: GET /quotations/open (Filters?)
    API-->>A: 200 OK (List includes quotationId)

    A->>API: POST /quotations/{quotationId}/offers (Offer Details)
    API-->>A: 201 Created (offerId)

    C->>API: GET /quotations/{quotationId} (View Details & Offers)
    API-->>C: 200 OK (Details + List of Offers including offerId)

    alt Offer Communication Loop
        C->>API: POST /quotations/{qId}/offers/{offerId}/messages (Msg Text, Optional Image)
        API-->>C: 200 OK (New Message Added)

        A->>API: POST /quotations/{qId}/offers/{offerId}/messages (Msg Text, Optional Image)
        API-->>A: 200 OK (New Message Added)
    end

    C->>API: POST /quotations/{qId}/offers/{offerId}/accept
    API-->>C: 200 OK (Offer Accepted, Status Updated)